commit.message:
alloc-pool.c (pool_alloc): Fix valgrind annotation.

2012-08-21  Richard Guenther  <rguenther@suse.de>

	* alloc-pool.c (pool_alloc): Fix valgrind annotation.
	* tree.h: Fix typo and complete flags documentation.

From-SVN: r190559
